title: idk how you can read this and NOT support Donald Trump.

embed.description: GOP candidate Donald Trump tells Bill O'Reilly tonight "I just sued Univision for $500 million" adding, "the papers were just filed so that will be interesting." The pre-taped interview will air on Fox News Channel's The O'Reilly Factor in about two hours.

body:
Only a bleeding heart liberal would disagree with what they said.

Quit being so politically correct or you'll get walked all over on.
